    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《7月14日》是一款灵异题材的恐怖悬疑解谜游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事发生在一栋房子里，家里的一些事情让丽莎觉得莫名的熟悉，她想要找到这种熟悉感的来源。在一次以外的通灵仪式之下，她似乎见到了谁，她离真相越来越近了......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >弗兰斯从昏迷中醒来，发现自己被困在着火的地下室中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >待到她从地下室逃脱，等待她的却是...... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >七月十四，到底意味着什么？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【故事】</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras/beeca9a9a917ee7d673cc5e8670b79d8.avif?t=1728631336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras_big/beeca9a9a917ee7d673cc5e8670b79d8.avif?t=1728631336 width=800 height=482 /></span>这是一个励志的故事，故事讲述了几个女孩，在一些难以磨灭的经历后如何重新振作起来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这又是一个悲惨的故事，这些经历，让她们永远被困在了这栋房子中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【角色】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras/b7ba86b7751a1213c3d899c767201d32.avif?t=1728631336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras_big/b7ba86b7751a1213c3d899c767201d32.avif?t=1728631336 width=800 height=360 /></span>玩家可以扮演三个角色，在不同年代不同视角下，经历相似的事情，破解同一个迷局。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阻挠她们的，或是家人，或是房子中奇怪的存在......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【场景】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高清化的场景，更能营造出阴暗诡异的氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大雾弥漫的室外。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras/ab3bcb429d0c2d66a41119821cc5a2bf.avif?t=1728631336\" width=766 height=432 /></span>花屏的电视。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras/eb78907909d48a7d7513f44abe7c1dba.avif?t=1728631336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras_big/eb78907909d48a7d7513f44abe7c1dba.avif?t=1728631336 width=800 height=476 /></span>发霉的木柜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras/8e4cea433a9f50202c15faed9c57e839.avif?t=1728631336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras_big/8e4cea433a9f50202c15faed9c57e839.avif?t=1728631336 width=800 height=480 /></span>烧黑的书架。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras/eb78907909d48a7d7513f44abe7c1dba.avif?t=1728631336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras_big/eb78907909d48a7d7513f44abe7c1dba.avif?t=1728631336 width=800 height=476 /></span><strong>【解谜】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras/d8823a337d60650525103defbe9c0e3c.avif?t=1728631336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras_big/d8823a337d60650525103defbe9c0e3c.avif?t=1728631336 width=800 height=360 /></span>谜题与剧情紧密结合，让剧情体验更加有趣。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras/db8b20ec151bfcda2e090d7fd1b56c15.poster.avif?t=1728631336\" width=800 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras/db8b20ec151bfcda2e090d7fd1b56c15.webm?t=1728631336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras/db8b20ec151bfcda2e090d7fd1b56c15.mp4?t=1728631336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于3D场景下的物品交互，更具真实感。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras/ff840aecb2da0d5e5557be451ac70435.avif?t=1728631336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093070/extras_big/ff840aecb2da0d5e5557be451ac70435.avif?t=1728631336 width=800 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灯光和场景的互动，通过光影的变化展现出谜题的多样性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三主角模式扩展了解谜的可能性，给这个故事增加些许趣味。</p>",
